Available Packages
Name       : exim
Arch       : i386
Version    : 4.63
Release    : 3.el5
Size       : 1.2 M
Repo       : base
Summary    : The exim mail transfer agent
URL        : http://www.exim.org/
License    : GPL
Description: Exim is a message transfer agent (MTA) developed at the University
           : of Cambridge for use on Unix systems connected to the Internet. It
           : is freely available under the terms of the GNU General Public
           : Licence. In style it is similar to Smail 3, but its facilities are
           : more general. There is a great deal of flexibility in the way mail
           : can be routed, and there are extensive facilities for checking
           : incoming mail. Exim can be installed in place of sendmail, although
           : the configuration of exim is quite different to that of sendmail.

